reviewText: Purchased as a gift. My daughter loved it. Arrived as promised.

All the songs performed by L'arc~en~Ciel on March 25th, 2012 at Madison Square Gardens, straddling two discs. You will need a multi-region or regionless DVD/Blu-ray player, but it is totally worth it! It's my first J-rock concert to own, and I'm so, so happy with my purchase!
